// Task 3555 / annotation-args δ fixture.
//
// `@shell(linear_taper(1.0))` carries a NON-literal expression argument. Lowering
// must preserve it as `AnnotationArg { name: None, value: Expr(<call linear_taper(1.0)>) }`
// rather than warn-and-drop it (the pre-δ behaviour). Validation still rejects the arg
// because @shell's Phase-1 schema accepts only a numeric-literal thickness — that schema
// mismatch is the observable proof the IR survived lowering far enough to reach validation.
@shell(linear_taper(1.0)) structure def Plate {
    param x : Real
}
